Description_lang: The Prototype of Absolution creates images of himself that mark random players, then charge to them $d later. Each image inflicts $327810s1 Physical damage and applies Touch of the Night to all players in their path, removing $@spellname366159.Upon reaching their target, Night Hunters strike with $@spellname361741.
AuraDescription_lang: Upon expiration, inflicts up to $327823s1 Physical damage and heals The Prototype of Absolution.
